description: Gets all of the variables or the specific variable. This is a paginated API. Providing null maxSizePerPage results in retrieving maximum of 100 records per page. If you provide maxSizePerPage the value must be between 50 and 100. To get the next page result, a provide a pagination token from GetVariablesResult as part of your request. Null pagination token fetches the records from the beginning.

nested_items.name: variables
nested_items.description: The names of the variables returned.

nested_items.name: dataType
nested_items.description: The data type of the variable. For more information see Variable types.

nested_items.name: dataSource
nested_items.description: The data source of the variable.

nested_items.name: defaultValue
nested_items.description: The default value of the variable.

nested_items.name: variableType
nested_items.description: The variable type of the variable.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The time when variable was last updated.

nested_items.name: createdTime
nested_items.description: The time when the variable was created.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next page token to be used in subsequent requests.
